		{"id":"523b142e5469095e","type":"text","text":"## Aperiodic Monoids\n\nA monoid is aperiodic if for all $x\\in M$ \n$$\\exists i.x^i = x^{i+1}$$","x":-400,"y":640,"width":360,"height":180},
